data.description: Flat, private .38 acre corner lot with room to expand. 3 bedroom with bonus 450 foot family room and sunroom so wonderful entertainment home. Wood floors, newly tiled master shower and updated kitchen with new appliances. Producing grape vines, above ground pool, outdoor entertainment kitchen, chicken coop and plenty of room for an ADU and room for RV, Boat, or toys.  Well cared for and move in ready.
